00:21:46.210 --> 00:21:49.870
people have tried it now,
and tried what it means.

00:21:50.070 --> 00:21:57.000
It showed potentials of individual segments and sectors
for change within the organization of work

00:21:57.200 --> 00:22:01.000
I'm not an economist, I'll leave all this
to Mrs professor and Mrs doctor

00:22:01.200 --> 00:22:05.950
to talk more about it.
But what I would like to say is that

00:22:06.150 --> 00:22:11.100
the interventions and the economic transformation,

00:22:11.300 --> 00:22:13.600
and the effects of closing down
