00:44:33.000 --> 00:44:36.100
And suddenly it was such a huge leap,
in the context of building

00:44:36.300 --> 00:44:40.670
those competencies of teachers,
to use, to master those tools, to be prepared,

00:44:40.870 --> 00:44:46.850
that it flexibly pushed the whole area.

00:44:47.050 --> 00:44:54.400
Now we have two such key changes in the level
of primary and secondary education,

00:44:54.600 --> 00:44:57.740
which relate to the transformation
of computer science teaching,

00:44:57.940 --> 00:45:04.260
