it was said across those panels,

00:45:48.900 --> 00:45:53.500
the competence of the public administration
to use its own administrative data,

00:45:53.700 --> 00:46:02.350
for being able to plan measures or use some tools,
is very limited.

00:46:02.550 --> 00:46:04.610
This is what the pandemic crisis has shown us,

00:46:04.810 --> 00:46:09.450
it also applies to education, it applies
to all other sectors and segments,

00:46:09.650 --> 00:46:11.382
and it is crucial to keep repeating it.

00:46:11.582 --> 00:46:18.700
It is not about swearing at the public
administration, that officials are incompetent,

00:46:18.900 --> 00:46:21.280
it is a political task that is missing.

00:46:21.480 --> 00:46:24.180
Nobody pushes it,
because nobody understands it.

00:46:24.380 --> 00:46:31.480
The senior management in that public
administration doesn't quite understand that either.

00:46:31.680 --> 00:46:34.714
That pressure is important, from above
, the political assignment,

00:46:34.914 --> 00:46:42.594
and from below, through actors such as
the public sector, non-profit organizations.

00:46:42.794 --> 00:46:45.000
it has been very successful in education,

00:46:45.200 --> 00:46:50.300
Or platforms that try to use
that data and interconnect it.

00:46:50.500 --> 00:46:55.000
The public administration does not easily
find the internal competencies

00:46:55.200 --> 00:47:00.150
and when it wants to find them, it often
outsources them, and it is not even advantageous,

00:47:00.350 --> 00:47:05.400
because the public contracts and competitions
fall into the captivity of suppliers.

00:47:05.600 --> 00:47:10.480
And it is important to comprehensively grasp
it all  and somehow connect, symbiosize it

00:47:10.680 --> 00:47:12.205
and create competencies
in that public administration,

00:47:12.405 --> 00:47:15.500
so that it can be then set up effectively.

00:47:15.700 --> 00:47:20.650
So we wouldn't have 150 unused billions,
or how many the doctor said,

00:47:20.850 --> 00:47:23.300
that were originally planned
to pour into the economy.

00:47:23.500 --> 00:47:26.200
In my opinion, they did not get there, because
the imagination of the Ministry of Finance

00:47:26.207 --> 00:47:31.520
is very limited and the Ministry of Industry
and Trade is not able to process it,

00:47:31.720 --> 00:47:34.600
but that is the my opinion of a clerk.

