00:48:17.200 --> 00:48:21.120
a huge counterweight to that other sector

00:48:21.320 --> 00:48:25.520
that has so far been quite negatively
affected by the covid,

00:48:25.720 --> 00:48:26.750
and that is the automotive industry.

