00:52:12.200 --> 00:52:18.900
So we have a public administration that has not
even started the process of digitization

00:52:19.100 --> 00:52:24.870
So the scissors during covid will open even more
than they were before the covid.

00:52:25.070 --> 00:52:29.250
Business and economics will completely
move away from that state administration.

00:52:29.450 --> 00:52:34.500
At this moment, the state administration
and its inability to digitize

00:52:34.700 --> 00:52:38.800
create institutional limits
for this business,

00:52:39.000 --> 00:52:42.200
but the state administration
also creates them for itself.

00:52:42.400 --> 00:52:53.180
If the digital sector is 8%, at the moment
many companies have a digital structure, etc.

00:52:53.380 --> 00:52:57.900
and we have a tax system that is 30 years old
and at the time it was created

00:52:58.100 --> 00:53:00.440
digital sector. didnt even existed

00:53:00.640 --> 00:53:07.100
So it is quite clear that the state will not
be able to tax the digital economy at all.

00:53:07.300 --> 00:53:11.500
Therefore, many of those activities
take place in the Czech Republic

00:53:11.700 --> 00:53:14.000
without the companies being
physically present here,

00:53:14.200 --> 00:53:18.200
and the whole concept of our taxation
is based on that physical presence.

00:53:18.400 --> 00:53:22.100
We just can't tax
the digital presence in the country.

00:53:22.300 --> 00:53:25.300
We are talking
about an absolutely fundamental change,

00:53:25.500 --> 00:53:29.550
a change of paradigm in the economy,
in all areas,

00:53:29.750 --> 00:53:35.500
And our problem is, that we have not been able
to do basic structural reforms for 30 years,

00:53:35.700 --> 00:53:39.700
and the accelerator accelerates the good,

00:53:39.900 --> 00:53:41.730
but on the other hand it reveals that bad.

00:53:41.930 --> 00:53:47.680
It revealed this here,
and if we are not able to respond to it,

00:53:47.880 --> 00:53:51.220
we will miss the train, but the most
importantly we will not be able

00:53:51.420 --> 00:53:53.150
to fix the hole in those public finances.

